@startuml

[*] --> UserRegistration
state Choice1 <<choice>>
UserRegistration : entry / Start state
UserRegistration : do / Fill in required details
UserRegistration : exit / Login

UserRegistration --> Login : registration complete

Login : entry / User registration
Login : do / Log in with credentials
Login : exit / Visa application

Login --> ApplyingForVisa : login successful

ApplyingForVisa : entry / Login
ApplyingForVisa : do / Apply for visa, make payment
ApplyingForVisa : exit / Application accepted

ApplyingForVisa --> PaymentConfirmation : application accepted

PaymentConfirmation : entry / Applying for visa
PaymentConfirmation : do / Wait for approval
PaymentConfirmation : exit / Status check

PaymentConfirmation --> Choice1

StatusChecking : entry / Applying for visa
StatusChecking : do / Check status of the application
StatusChecking : exit / Decision making

Choice1 --> ApprovedVisa : approved
Choice1 --> RejectedVisa : rejected

ApprovedVisa : entry / Status check
ApprovedVisa : do / Update status to approved
ApprovedVisa : exit / Feedback

ApprovedVisa --> GivingFeedback

RejectedVisa : entry / Status check
RejectedVisa : do / Update status to rejected
RejectedVisa : exit / Logout

RejectedVisa --> Logout

GivingFeedback : entry / Approved visa
GivingFeedback : do / Give feedback
GivingFeedback : exit / Logout

GivingFeedback --> Logout

Logout : entry / Giving feedback or completing status update
Logout : do / Log out
Logout : exit / final state

Logout --> [*]

@enduml
